This paper discusses the convergence rate of evolutionary algorithms, which is a topic related to optimization and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves the classification of solution generation strategies, which can be considered as a topic in data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the analysis of convergence rate involves theoretical proofs, which can be categorized as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems and control (cs.SY).
